n from swimming but she was never considered among Britain's top medal prospects here.\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3495, \"end\": 3503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Cashmore_Ltd\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cashmore\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Cashmore_Ltd\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Cashmore_Ltd\"}, {\"begin\": 3508, \"end\": 3516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christina_Stead\", \"score\": 0.7090278419348949, \"rank\": 0.4103818248833327, \"text\": \"Steadman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christina_Stead\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christina_Stead\"}, {\"begin\": 3601, \"end\": 3608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9104671992351961, \"rank\": 0.09833676993299238, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Richter\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"triathlon\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3551}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 3557, \"to\": 3565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She arguably benefited from the absence of American favourite Kelly Elmlinger, who withdrew hours before the race, but being good and lucky is always key to success.\", \"from\": 3637, \"to\": 3802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3680, \"end\": 3688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999757424124, \"rank\": 1.2963797021438001e-08, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3699, \"end\": 3704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Kapoor\", \"score\": 0.9728201742304455, \"rank\": 0.0279